@node "Bugs" "Bugs"

                               @{u}Bugs@{uu}

The program has gone through extensive testing and is used in every-day
situations on the @{"author's" link "Author"} system and have thus far run impeckably.

Due to the nature of programming however, there are bound to be some
lurking in the code somewhere. Should you believe you have found one,
do please send the @{"author" link "Author"} an E-Mail stating as much information as
possible such as what button and/or configuration line causes the error
and also a copy of the letter the script was runned on if possible.
@endnode

